          .col-sm-10 Dancing!

.rsvp-section.row#travel
  .rsvp-icon.col-md-5
    = svg('wedding/Airplane')
    | Travel

  .section-info.col-md-7
    .row
      .col-md-2
        = svg('wedding/Airport')
      .col-md-10
        h3 Getting here
        p We recommend flying through the Oakland International Airport. From there you can take a train to the Oakland Coliseum BART station, which will get you to Berkeley. If you are staying at the HOTEL, you may want to call a Lyft to get there, as public transportation to the HOTEL is limited.
    .row
      .col-md-2
        = svg('wedding/Transportation')
      .col-md-10
        h3 Getting around
        p We'll have a shuttle to take you to and from the wedding if you're staying in our hotel block.
        p Otherwise, we recommend using Lyft to get to the Brazilian Room.
    .row
      .col-md-2
        = svg('wedding/Hotel')
      .col-md-10
        h3 Where to stay
        p We have a limited number of rooms with the #{link_to('Double Tree at the Berkeley Marina', 'doubleTreeLink', target: '_blank')}.
        p We also recommend:
        p
          = link_to('Holiday Inn Express on University', 'holidayInn', target: '_blank')
        p
          = link_to('La Quinta Inn on University', 'laQuinta', target: '_blank')
    .row
      .col-md-2
        = svg('wedding/Food')
      .col-md-10
        h3 Things to eat
        p =link_to("Barney's Burgers", 'barneyBurgers', target: '_blank')
        p Delicious burgers in a variety of styles with good vegetarian options. We love their milkshakes!
        p =link_to('Royal Cafe' 'royalCafe', target: '_blank')
        p Classic kitchsy diner cafe with great food. Laurel loves their pancakes.
        p =link_to('Super Super Pho', 'superSuper', target: '_blank')
        p We eat here all the time


.rsvp-section.row#qna
  .rsvp-icon.col-md-5
    = svg('wedding/Q_A')
    | Q & A
  .section-info.col-md-7

    strong When is the RSVP deadline?
    p We'd appreciate if you RSVP'd by this date

    strong Can I bring a date?
    p Please do! We'd love to meet your date. Just be sure to include them in your RSVP.

    strong Are kids welcome?
    p Yep!

    strong What time should I arrive?
    p 6pm

    strong How should I get there? Where should I park?
    p There is a parking lot on site. blahblah

    strong Is the Brazil Room wheelchair accessible?
    p I hope so

    strong What should I wear?
    p Filthy casual

    strong Who should I contact with questions?
    p If you have any questions or concerns, please let us know at #{link_to('mailto: wedding@example.com')}

.rsvp-section.row#photos
  .rsvp-icon.col-md-5
    = svg('wedding/Photo')
    | Photos
  .section-info.col-md-7
    p We'd love to see the photos you take! We've set up a drive you can submit to if you'd like to share.
    =link_to('Photo drive', class: 'btn-link')
    p You can also use the hashtag <strong>#lovegarden2020</strong> on social media so we can see your pics.

